a:3:{s:11:"notes_total";i:6;s:11:"notes_ctree";a:6:{i:0;a:32:{s:2:"id";i:53;s:5:"title";s:54:"Attio ships a bundle of platform and design updates";s:4:"href";s:81:"https://weekcrm.com/blog/all/attio-ships-a-bundle-of-platform-and-design-updates/";s:13:"href-original";s:81:"https://weekcrm.com/blog/all/attio-ships-a-bundle-of-platform-and-design-updates/";s:4:"time";a:2:{i:0;i:1768831200;i:1;a:2:{s:6:"offset";i:18000;s:6:"is_dst";b:0;}}s:13:"last-modified";a:2:{i:0;i:1768570299;i:1;a:2:{s:6:"offset";i:18000;s:6:"is_dst";b:0;}}s:4:"text";s:829:"<p>Attio’s update includes multiple small-to-mid changes across workspace settings, billing, referrals, and file handling.</p>
<h3>What changed</h3>
<p>Attio now allows slug reuse for deleted workspaces, adds a configurable workspace accent color, and streamlines billing flows for plan selection, extra invites, automation credits, and checkout. Referral tooling was updated with a new CTA, revamped Refer and earn page, quick-share links with preset copy, and an anonymized referral list with status indicators.</p>
<h3>Files and attachments</h3>
<p>Attio also redesigned file storage: refreshed Files tab UI, migration to an S3-style backend, attachment support across all record types (including Deals), and improved image rendering. A small site UI tweak allows copying the logo as an SVG via hover.</p>
";s:11:"format-info";a:2:{s:14:"links-required";a:0:{}s:18:"resources-detected";a:0:{}}s:7:"summary";s:87:"Attio ships a bundle of platform and design updates | Read fresh CRM news on WeekCRM";s:12:"snippet-text";s:87:"Attio ships a bundle of platform and design updates | Read fresh CRM news on WeekCRM";s:6:"draft?";b:0;s:10:"scheduled?";b:0;s:7:"public?";b:1;s:7:"hidden?";b:0;s:8:"current?";b:0;s:10:"favourite?";b:0;s:6:"images";a:0:{}s:6:"thumbs";a:0:{}s:21:"source-main-image-url";s:0:"";s:9:"og-images";a:0:{}s:16:"og-images-thumbs";a:0:{}s:4:"tags";a:3:{i:0;a:4:{s:8:"visible?";b:1;s:4:"name";s:5:"attio";s:4:"href";s:35:"http://weekcrm.com/blog/tags/attio/";s:8:"current?";b:1;}i:1;a:4:{s:8:"visible?";b:1;s:4:"name";s:3:"CRM";s:4:"href";s:33:"http://weekcrm.com/blog/tags/crm/";s:8:"current?";b:0;}i:2;a:4:{s:8:"visible?";b:1;s:4:"name";s:15:"product updates";s:4:"href";s:45:"http://weekcrm.com/blog/tags/product-updates/";s:8:"current?";b:0;}}s:15:"sharing-buttons";b:0;s:7:"related";b:0;s:9:"read-href";s:86:"https://weekcrm.com/blog/all/attio-ships-a-bundle-of-platform-and-design-updates/read/";s:12:"preview-href";b:0;s:14:"comments-count";i:0;s:19:"comments-count-text";s:9:"0 comment";s:18:"new-comments-count";b:0;s:23:"new-comments-count-text";s:0:"";s:14:"comments-link?";b:1;s:13:"href-comments";s:90:"https://weekcrm.com/blog/all/attio-ships-a-bundle-of-platform-and-design-updates/#comments";}i:1;a:32:{s:2:"id";i:52;s:5:"title";s:47:"Attio App Store adds Productboard and JustCall";s:4:"href";s:76:"https://weekcrm.com/blog/all/attio-app-store-adds-productboard-and-justcall/";s:13:"href-original";s:76:"https://weekcrm.com/blog/all/attio-app-store-adds-productboard-and-justcall/";s:4:"time";a:2:{i:0;i:1768744800;i:1;a:2:{s:6:"offset";i:18000;s:6:"is_dst";b:0;}}s:13:"last-modified";a:2:{i:0;i:1768570035;i:1;a:2:{s:6:"offset";i:18000;s:6:"is_dst";b:0;}}s:4:"text";s:383:"<p>Attio released two new App Store integrations: Productboard and JustCall. Productboard is positioned for pushing customer insights from Attio into Productboard, while JustCall connects business calling to Attio and automatically logs calls, texts, voicemails, and AI insights.</p>
<p>Learn more here: <a href="https://attio.com/changelog">https://attio.com/changelog</a></p>
